<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div id="overlay" class="overlay"></div>
    <button id="toggleBtn" class="toggle-arrow">
        <span>Book Appointment</span><i></i>
    </button>
    <section id="appointmentSection">
        <%- include('partials/appointmentForm') %>
        <br><br>
    </section>

    <div class="container2">
        <div>
            <h1>BBMH Hospital â€“ Advanced Eye Care and Vision Correction in Bhilwara</h1>
            <img src="\images\eye.jpg" alt="" class="img">
            <p>
                At BBMH Hospital, our Ophthalmology Department offers cutting-edge eye care services with a focus on precision, safety, and patient comfort. We specialize in diagnosing and treating a wide range of eye conditions including cataracts, glaucoma, diabetic retinopathy, and refractive errors such as myopia, hyperopia, and astigmatism. Our state-of-the-art equipment and skilled ophthalmologists ensure high-quality care for patients of all ages. With comprehensive eye exams, surgical interventions like LASIK and cataract removal, and advanced vision correction techniques, BBMH is dedicated to preserving and enhancing your eyesight.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2>Common Eye Conditions Treated:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><b>Cataracts:</b> Clouding of the eye lens, leading to blurred or dim vision.</li>
                <li><b>Glaucoma:</b> A group of eye conditions that damage the optic nerve, often linked to high intraocular pressure.</li>
                <li><b>Refractive Errors:</b> Vision problems like nearsightedness, farsightedness, and astigmatism corrected through glasses, lenses, or surgery.</li>
                <li><b>Diabetic Retinopathy:</b> Damage to retinal blood vessels due to diabetes, which may lead to blindness if untreated.</li>
                <li><b>Dry Eye Syndrome:</b> A condition caused by decreased tear production or poor-quality tears, leading to irritation and redness.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="container3">
        <div class="wrapper" style="margin-top: 8vh;">
            <img src="\images\eye2.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="intro">
                <h2>Advanced Cataract Surgery</h2>
                <p>Our ophthalmologists perform minimally invasive cataract surgeries using the latest phacoemulsification technique, ensuring quicker recovery and improved visual outcomes. Patients can choose from a range of intraocular lenses for better clarity and reduced dependence on glasses.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="wrapper1">
            <img src="\images\eye3.jpeg" alt="">
            <div class="intro1">
                <h2>LASIK Vision Correction</h2>
                <p>BBMH offers LASIK surgery for permanent vision correction. This safe and painless procedure reshapes the cornea using a laser, correcting refractive errors and reducing reliance on corrective eyewear.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="wrapper2">
            <img src="\images\eye4.jpeg" alt="">
            <div class="intro2">
                <h2>Retina Care</h2>
                <p>Our retina specialists are skilled in treating complex retinal diseases like macular degeneration and diabetic retinopathy. With diagnostic imaging and laser treatments, we ensure the best outcomes for retinal health and vision preservation.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
            document.getElementById("toggleBtn").addEventListener("click", function () {
                let appointmentSection = document.getElementById("appointmentSection");
                appointmentSection.style.display = (appointmentSection.style.display === "none" || appointmentSection.style.display === "") ? "block" : "none";
            });
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
            document.getElementById("toggleBtn").addEventListener("click", function () {
                window.scrollTo({
                    top: 10,
                    behavior: "smooth"
                });
            });
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        (() => {
            'use strict';
            const forms = document.querySelectorAll('.needs-validation');
            Array.from(forms).forEach(form => {
                form.addEventListener('submit', event => {
                    if (!form.checkValidity()) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        event.stopPropagation();
                    }
                    form.classList.add('was-validated');
                }, false);
            });
        })();
    </script>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/gsap.min.js" integrity="sha512-7eHRwcbYkK4d9g/6tD/mhkf++eoTHwpNM9woBxtPUBWm67zeAfFC+HrdoE2GanKeocly/VxeLvIqwvCdk7qScg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/ScrollTrigger.min.js" integrity="sha512-onMTRKJBKz8M1TnqqDuGBlowlH0ohFzMXYRNebz+yOcc5TQr/zAKsthzhuv0hiyUKEiQEQXEynnXCvNTOk50dg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></script>
    <script src="index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>